testcase.name: Updating a subject that exists updates the subject()
Deleting an existing subject removes it from the Array List()
Deleting a non-existent subject returns null (error handling)()
Trying to update a subject that doesn't exist returns false()
Adding a subject to an empty array list adds to the list()
Adding a subject to a populated array list adds to the list()
When the viewSubjects function is invoked on an empty list, a string is returned()
When the viewSubjects function is invoked on a populated list, notes are returned()
